The '''[[w:Integration law for new immigrants to the Netherlands|Integration law for new immigrants to the Netherlands]]''' (Dutch:inburgeringswet) can be distinguished between a course while still living abroad and courses while living in the Netherlands. Both are mandatory for certain classes of non-[[w:European Union|European Union]] citizens who live in the Netherlands or wish to live in the Netherlands.

*[[/English Basic|Inburgeringscurus (abroad) for English speakers]] (very basic level)
*[[/English Advanced|Inburgeringscurus (Netherlands) for English speakers]] (ranging from basic to several higher levels)

