{{Computer Science Index}}
The case study is part of paper 2 for both SL and HL students, and they share the same case study and some of the questions, but not all.

The case study itself if a real life problem or system, and the tasks the students are asked to perform are of analysis and design. e.g. suitable data structures of the system in the case study.

